import React from 'react'
import { config } from '@gluestack-ui/config'
import { GluestackUIProvider, Text, Card, Heading, Box } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'

const MusicList = (props) => {
    return (
        <GluestackUIProvider config={config}>
            <Card size="md" m="$1" style={{backgroundColor:'#292929'}}>
                <Box w='$5' h='$20' bg='$blue700' style={{ alignItems: 'baseline',borderRadius:10 }} />
                <Heading mb="$1" size="md" style={props.style}>
                    Quick Start
                </Heading>
            </Card>


        </GluestackUIProvider>
    )
}

export default MusicList
